    "rich_text_L6tA4g": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "text_Nc3LE8": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>When you browse our vast selection of lifelike silk florals and artificial plants, you'll not only find gorgeous botanical decorations for every style of interior décor, but for every season as well. </p><p>Enjoy the ever-changing floral seasons, from the fresh blooming appeal of spring tulips, cherry blossoms, and forsythia to the vibrant colors of summer lilies, daisies, roses, and hydrangeas. </p><p>Delight in the warmth of the fiery hues of autumn leaves and the joy of the festive colors of holiday designs that make your fall and winter gatherings truly memorable. No matter how you choose to decorate for a fresh seasonal look, you'll find that natural beauty abounds in our seasonal silk floral collections. Remember to save our quality shipping boxes for out-of-season storage to protect your seasonal designs for next year's enjoyment.</p>",
            "number_of_lines_shown": "none",
            "read_more_label": "Read more",
            "see_less_label": "See less"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "text_Nc3LE8"
      ],
